	&bull; Expert knowledge developing and debugging in C/C++, MySql.<br />
	&bull; Strong experience with server-side programming.<br />
	&bull; Experience in Memcached, Membase, Couchbase is a plus.<br />
	&bull; Experience with scripting languages such as Perl, Python, PHP, Ruby and shell scripts.<br />
	&bull; Extensive knowledge of Unix/Linux environments.<br />
	&bull; Knowledge of TCP/IP and network programming.<br />
	&bull; Experience with Git.</p>
<p>
