	Viralheat is a venture-backed social media analytics and intelligence firm based in San Mateo, California. Viralheat is a powerful, simple, yet affordable way for brands, agencies, marketers and content producers to measure, analyze and engage the social web. Viralheat&#39;s intelligence platform is connecting businesses, large and small, to the social web and changing the way business is done.</p>
